data.description: Welcome home to Horizon Peak! This home is perfect for a family in need of multiple living spaces to relax or entertain, 4 bedrooms with a potential office or flex room, high ceilings with tons of windows providing natural light, ceramic tile on the first floor easy to maintain/clean and a wood burning fireplace in family room for the cooler cozy nights!  Not to mention a 3-car garage with ample space for vehicles/ storage and a nice corner lot with lots of room out back to add your personal touch. This home truly has is ALL!
